          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Rajkumar Muppidi serves as the Chief Operating Officer (COO) of Addanki’s Food Stories Pvt. Ltd., where he leads the company’s operational strategy, supply chain execution, and distribution development across multiple business verticals.</p>",
            "font_family": "arimo_n4",
